ients\",\"grid\",\"hover effects\",\"logos\",\"partners\",\"responsive\",\"slider\",\"sponsors\",\"tooltips\"]},{\"id\":11445580,\"name\":\"Tables for Layers - Layers Extension\",\"description\":\"\\nTables for Layers &#8211; An Easy to Use Table Manager for Layers\\n\\nTables for Layers is an easy to use and simple table manager made for Layers to create, manage and design tables for your Layers Theme.\\n\\n\\nTables for Layers provide a simple Excel-like interface with the ability to add/edit/remove rows and columns. It also provide the basic styling features for the Table integrated with the Layers Design Bar.\\n\\n\\nList of Features\\n\\nEasy to use Excel-like interface for editing tables.\\nAdd/Remove Rows and Columns\\nLayers Styling Options for your Table\\n\\n\\nVersion Log\\n\\nVersion 1.0 - 13/05/2015\\n- Initial Release\\n\",\"description_html\":\"<p><a href=\\\"http://enva.to/2Hhv8\\\" rel=\\\"nofollow\\\"><img src=\\\"http://all-marketplaces.s3.amazonaws.com/growth/layers/landing-badge-small.png\\\" /></a></p>\\n<h2 id=\\\"item-description__tables-for-layers-an-easy-to-use-table-manager-for-layers\\\">Tables for Layers &#8211; An Easy to Use Table Manager for Layers</h2>\\n\\n<p>Tables for Layers is an easy to use and simple table manager made for <a href=\\\"http://www.layerswp.com\\\" rel=\\\"nofollow\\\">Layers</a> to create, manage and design tables for your Layers Theme.\\n</p>\\n\\n<p>Tables for Layers provide a simple Excel-like interface with the ability to add/edit/remove rows and columns. It also provide the basic styling features for the Table integrated with the Layers Design Bar.\\n</p>\\n\\n<h2 id=\\\"item-description__list-of-features\\\">List of Features</h2>\\n<ul>\\n<li>Easy to use Excel-like interface for editing tables.</li>\\n<li>Add/Remove Rows and Columns</li>\\n<li>Layers Styling Options for your Table</li>\\n</ul>\\n\\n<h2 id=\\\"item-description__version-log\\\">Version Log</h2>\\n<pre>\\nVersion 1.0 - 13/05/2015\\n- Initial R