 to your website. With this plugin you can create video outstanding video galleries on your website (check out the demo website: http://youtuber.maxiolab.com/).\\n\\nCustomer reviews:\\n\\n\\nWhy should you buy YouTubeR:\\n\\n    easy upload videos on YouTube from your WordPress website\\n    easy embed YouTube videos to your WordPress website\\n    create video galleries\\n    fully responsive layout\\n    Visual Composer integrated\\n    infinite scroll for playlists\\n    optimized for WordPress caching\\n    supports cyrillic characters\\n    customizable responsiveness\\n    full control over plugin theme\",\"description_html\":\"<p><img src=\\\"http://youtuber.maxiolab.com/codecanyon/f-2.png\\\" alt=\\\"Visual Composer integrated\\\" /></p>\\n<p><img src=\\\"http://youtuber.maxiolab.com/codecanyon/f-3.png\\\" alt=\\\"Fully compatible with WPML\\\" /></p>\\n<p><a href=\\\"http://youtuber.maxiolab.com/docs/\\\" rel=\\\"nofollow\\\"><img src=\\\"http://youtuber.maxiolab.com/codecanyon/f-4.png\\\" alt=\\\"Online documentation\\\" /></a></p>\\n<p><a href=\\\"http://youtuber.maxiolab.com/playlist-templates/\\\" rel=\\\"nofollow\\\"><img src=\\\"http://youtuber.maxiolab.com/codecanyon/f-5.png\\\" alt=\\\"Awesome templates included\\\" /></a></p>\\n<p><img src=\\\"http://youtuber.maxiolab.com/codecanyon/f-6.png\\\" alt=\\\"Fully responsive layout\\\" /></p>\\n\\n<p>YouTubeR &#8211; <strong>unique</strong> WordPress plugin, that allows you to upload videos on YouTube from your website and to easily embed YouTube videos, playlists, channels to your website. With this plugin you can create video outstanding video galleries on your website (check out the demo website: <a href=\\\"http://youtuber.maxiolab.com/\\\" rel=\\\"nofollow\\\">http://youtuber.maxiolab.com/</a>).</p>\\n\\n<h2 id=\\\"item-description__customer-reviews\\\">Customer reviews:</h2>\\n<img src=\\\"http://youtuber.maxiolab.com/codecanyon/testimonials.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"Customer reviews\\\" />\\n\\n<h2 id=\\\"