-shop_catalog size-shop_catalog wp-post-image\" alt=\"facebook\" /></a>\n\n	<h2>\n	<span class=\"price\"><span class=\"amount\">$19</span></span>\n <a href=\"https://wpjobmanager.com/add-ons/apply-with-facebook/\">Apply with Facebook</a></h2>\n\n	<p>Allow candidates to apply to jobs via email using their Facebook profile.</p>\n</li>\n				\n					<li class=\"post-5046 product type-product status-publish has-post-thumbnail product_cat-core-add-ons product_cat-functionality pa_license-developer pa_license-personal virtual sold-individually taxable shipping-taxable purchasable product-type-variable product-cat-core-add-ons product-cat-functionality has-default-attributes has-children instock\">\n	<a href=\"https://wpjobmanager.com/add-ons/apply-xing/\">\n	</a><a href=\"https://wpjobmanager.com/add-ons/apply-xing/\" class=\"item\">\n		<img width=\"318\" height=\"222\" src=\"https://wpjobmanager.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/xinglogo.png?resize=318%2C222\" class=\"attachment-shop_catalog size-shop_catalog wp-post-image\" alt=\"xinglogo\" /></a>\n\n	<h2>\n	<span class=\"price\"><span class=\"amount\">$19</span></span>\n <a href=\"https://wpjobmanager.com/add-ons/apply-xing/\">Apply with XING</a></h2>\n\n	<p>Allow candidates to apply to jobs via email using their XING profile.</p>\n</li>\n				\n					<li class=\"last post-730 product type-product status-publish has-post-thumbnail product_cat-core-add-ons product_cat-functionality pa_license-developer pa_license-personal virtual sold-individually taxable shipping-taxable purchasable product-type-variable product-cat-core-add-ons product-cat-functionality has-default-attributes has-children instock\">\n	<a href=\"https://wpjobmanager.com/add-ons/bookmarks/\">\n	</a><a href=\"https://wpjobmanager.com/add-ons/bookmarks/\" class=\"item\">\n		<img width=\"318\" height=\"222\" src=\"https://wpjobmanager.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/bookmarks1.png?resize=318%2C222\" class=\"attachment-shop_catalog size-shop_catalog wp-post-image\"