uct-cat-free product-cat-importexport instock\">\n	<a href=\"https://wpjobmanager.com/add-ons/wp-all-import-integration/\">\n	</a><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-job-manager-xml-csv-listings-import/\" class=\"item\">\n		<img width=\"318\" height=\"222\" src=\"https://wpjobmanager.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/WPAI-WPJM-ADDON.png?resize=318%2C222\" class=\"attachment-shop_catalog size-shop_catalog wp-post-image\" alt=\"WPAI-WPJM-ADDON\" /><span class=\"third_party\">3rd Party</span>	</a>\n\n	<h2>\n	<span class=\"price\"><span class=\"amount\">Free!</span></span>\n <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-job-manager-xml-csv-listings-import/\">WP All Import Integration</a></h2>\n\n	<p>Easily import job listings from any XML or CSV file to the WP Job Manager plugin with the WP Job Manager Add-On for WP All Import.</p>\n</li>\n				\n					<li class=\"last post-5387 product type-product status-publish has-post-thumbnail product_cat-core-add-ons product_cat-functionality pa_license-developer pa_license-personal virtual sold-individually taxable shipping-taxable purchasable product-type-variable product-cat-core-add-ons product-cat-functionality has-default-attributes has-children instock\">\n	<a href=\"https://wpjobmanager.com/add-ons/embeddable-job-widget/\">\n	</a><a href=\"https://wpjobmanager.com/add-ons/embeddable-job-widget/\" class=\"item\">\n		<img width=\"318\" height=\"222\" src=\"https://wpjobmanager.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/embed-widget.png?resize=318%2C222\" class=\"attachment-shop_catalog size-shop_catalog wp-post-image\" alt=\"embed-widget\" /></a>\n\n	<h2>\n	<span class=\"price\"><span class=\"amount\">$19</span></span>\n <a href=\"https://wpjobmanager.com/add-ons/embeddable-job-widget/\">Embeddable Job Widget</a></h2>\n\n	<p>Show a form on your site that users can use to generate an embeddable job widget showing job listings from your site.</p>\n</li>\n				\n					<li class=\"first post-2242 product type-product status-publish has-post-t